---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="christian legge" mainClass="max-w-[65ch] animate-fade-up-in">
	<h1 class="text-center text-2xl font-light">christianlegge.dev</h1>
	<p>
		welcome to my website. there isn't much going on here, but if you ended
		up here, i guess you want to know what's up.
	</p>
	<p>
		writing code is like my main thing. i've been doing it for a long time.
		i learned html on neopets like everyone my age did, but i wrote my first
		"real" line of code when i was 13. i have around 10 years of
		professional experience and lots more doing hobby projects.
	</p>
	<p>
		it also feels pretty pertinent to mention up top here that i'm <strong
			><em>very strongly anti-AI</em></strong
		>. hopefully in the future that becomes less important to say. i don't
		use chatgpt, or claude, or copilot or whatever the newest thing that
		can't write good code is. i write my own code, i write it well, and my
		skills aren't hemorrhaging as a result of shifting my daily routine to
		arguing with a chatbot. you can read more of my thoughts on that here,
		if you want.
	</p>
	<p>
		like many others of my ilk, i'm not allowed to call myself an engineer
		in this country due to strict licensing protections. but i have an
		engineering degree and i have lots of experience performing the job of a
		typical software engineer. i started my career in low-level
		infrastructure, but always enjoyed web development more, and that's most
		of what i do nowadays.
	</p>
	<p>
		i like to write sometimes. i put a blog section on this site expecting
		to use it for, like, tech stuff, but it's mostly just been personal
		essays. i don't contribute to it with any sort of regularity, but it's
		there.
	</p>
	<p>
		guess that's about it. feel free to look around the rest of the site. if
		you want to contact me, you can do so at [firstname] at
		christianlegge.dev.
	</p>
	<p>free palestine.</p>
</Layout>
<style>
	p {
		@apply mt-2;
	}
	h3 {
		@apply text-3xl font-medium;
	}
	.cutout {
		@apply my-4 inline-block rotate-3 border-4 border-dashed border-green-700 border-opacity-50 bg-white px-1 font-bold shadow-xl;
	}
	li {
		@apply my-2 list-inside list-disc text-xl;
	}
	section {
		@apply mx-auto mt-4 max-w-[100ch];
	}
	section > h3 {
		@apply ml-auto mr-0 text-right;
	}
	section > ul {
		@apply text-left;
	}
</style>
